
YAC - Your Automated Cloud v{VER}
{COMMAND}

Available comands include:

  yac {COMMAND} (-h | primer)

* -h provides cli help
* primer will display this page

Test executes a series of integration tests against a service in a given pipeline stage.

Say the 'platformengineering/redis:4.6' service has three stages in its pipeline:

* dev
* test
* prod

Say you have already built the 'platformengineering/redis:4.6' service in the dev stage, and you want to run its integration tests.

Run the tests as:

$ yac test platformengineering/redis:4.6